<div class="sub-content-header">How Many Attendees Plan to Visit Your Booth?  </div>
<br />


<P><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'"><IMG height=90 hspace=10 src="/images/content/myces.gif" width=150 align=right>Get your booth added to attendees’ Event Plans by increasing your visibility on the MyCES Personal Planner. Adding online video to your company listing is one quick and easy way to enhance your online presence. Plus, by including your video footage in supplier search results, your listings are sure to stand out from other exhibitors’ standard text links.<BR><BR></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'">The more attendees that find your business, the more event plans you appear on – resulting in increased traffic to your booth and business for your company. <BR><BR></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'">Post your video footage today. Contact Ed Gorey at 410-402-1070 or </SPAN><A href="mailto:ed.gorey@bdmetrics.com" target=_blank><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'">ed.gorey@bdmetrics.com</SPAN></A><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'">.</SPAN></P>
        <br /><img width="1" height="20" src="/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/images/framework/divider-line.gif"/><br />

<a name="2569"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">Free CES Exhibitor Activities: Sign-Up Now!</div>
<br />

<IMG height=43 hspace=10 src="/images/content/techEM.jpg" width=182 align=right vspace=10>Tech-EM.com, the online portal focused on trends and best practices for tradeshow managers and event marketers in the tech space, is once again partnering with CES on a variety of activities and content offers just for our exhibitors. Sign up for this year's FREE Exhibitor Activities: 
<UL class=text>
<LI class=text>THE CES100. The top 100 booths, moments, experiences. </LI>
<LI class=text>THE DAILY DOSE. The daily recap you can't miss. </LI>
<LI class=text>Video fly-throughs from your booth. </LI>
<LI class=text>Chance to Win! Booth audits and exhibit portraits. </LI>
<LI class=text>Press tours of your booth. </LI>
<LI class=text>Q&amp;As with top exhibitors.</LI></UL>...and more!Sign up at <A href="http://www.tech-em.com/webform/ces%2B2009%2Bactivity%2Bsign%2Bpage" target=_blank>tech-em.com/ces09</A>.
        <br /><img width="1" height="20" src="/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/images/framework/divider-line.gif"/><br />

<a name="2568"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">CNET Best of CES Awards</div>
<br />

<IMG height=115 hspace=10 src="/images/content/CNET.jpg" width=60 align=right vspace=10>CNET will host the 4th annual Best of CES Awards. Be sure to submit your product for consideration today! The deadline for submissions is December 8, 2008 – only a week away. Finalists will be announced 10 a.m. Friday, January 9, and winners will be announced at a live ceremony at the CNET Stage at 11 a.m. Saturday, January 10.. This year, winners will benefit from a congratulatory campaign across CBS Interactive and CBS properties. 
<P>For awards submission and information, visit <A href="http://www.cnet.com/best-of-ces" target=_blank>www.cnet.com/best-of-ces</A>.<BR></P>
        <br /><img width="1" height="20" src="/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/images/framework/divider-line.gif"/><br />

<a name="2611"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">The CES Daily--produced by TWICE--The Only Official Daily of CES. Closing this Week!</div>
<br />

<IMG height=41 hspace=10 src="/images/content/twice.gif" width=150 align=right vspace=10>With more than 2,700 exhibitors, it makes sense to shout to let show goers know you're there. Why not let an ad in the 2009 International CES Daily do the shouting for you? 4 issues, one low price -- massive distribution. Space closing this week. Don't get lost in the crowd. Call for discounted TWICE/ CES DAILY show packages.&nbsp; 646-746-6980. 
