<a name="2567"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">D&amp;H Distributing: Delivering Digital Lifestyle Solutions to the CE Channel</div>
<br />

<A href="https://www.dandh.com/v4/view?pageReq=dhmainns" target=_blank><IMG height=151 hspace=10 src="/images/content/DH.gif" width=125 align=right vspace=10 border=0>D&amp;H</A> brings to the channel an emerging technology leadership through a multi-category product selection spanning consumer electronics and video gaming to IT products and peripherals, with an impressive 90-year history serving as a consultative partner and trusted advisor. D&amp;H backs its multi-market expertise with account-dedicated service and comprehensive web resources.
        <br /><img width="1" height="20" src="/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/images/framework/divider-line.gif"/><br />

<a name="2566"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">Exhibit in the Technology and Emerging Countries TechZone</div>
<br />

<IMG height=91 hspace=10 src="/images/content/TEC.jpg" width=200 align=right vspace=5>Are you a manufacturer or organization that offers products and/or services to support the spread of technology in emerging countries? <BR><BR>Then take advantage of the opportunity to showcase your products at the 2009 International CES as part of the <A href="/exhibits/displays/techZones.asp" target=_blank>Technology and Emerging Countries (TEC) TechZone</A>. Participating companies will display the innovations that make it possible for every person on this planet to make use of technology and benefit from growing CE advances. Foundations and NGOs engaged in disseminating this technology to rural communities are also encouraged to participate.<BR><BR>For more information on how you can capitalize on this unique opportunity, contact Chris Amos at 703-907-7640 or <A href="mailto:camos@CE.org">camos@CE.org</A>.
        <br /><img width="1" height="20" src="/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
